{"tid":1954166,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國黨媒問你最愛的湖北菜　結果捉蟲被「蝙蝠湯」洗版","createTime":"2020-04-01T15:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T15:51:37.000Z","uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f978ed43bf69472ee184c5e782c783308e074ee0","tid":1954166,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2020/04/chinese-hubei-is-full-of-bat-soup/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2020%2F04%2Fchinese-hubei-is-full-of-bat-soup%2F&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUjw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=9e8d8f51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2020/04/chinese-hubei-is-full-of-bat-soup/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/global-times-china-bat-soup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fglobal-times-china-bat-soup.jpg&h=b03c85fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/global-times-china-bat-soup2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fglobal-times-china-bat-soup2.jpg&h=3787d29d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國政府近日極大做大外宣，向外界稱中國已經恢復正常，不再受武漢肺炎影響，又講食又慶祝等活動不停。可是，除了有外國媒體拍到中國的濕貨野味市場又再次開幕，售賣蝙蝠和狗等。中國的黨媒Global Times亦不放手，努力做好宣傳工作，在官方Twitter稱湖北人生活返回正常，問大家最愛的湖北菜是什麼。<br />\n<br />\n可惜的是，全球愈來愈多人明白今次武漢肺炎的始作俑者，有很多印度的朋友在Twitter上回應「蝙蝠湯」和其他的野味，明顯狂串中國。亦有很多網民貼上一系列的圖片狂串和罵中國，不知道Global Times發此文章的人，會否後悔？<br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/globaltimesnews/status/1244556983987888130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobaltimesnews%2Fstatus%2F1244556983987888130&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUjw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=f3460d3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobaltimesnews%2Fstatus%2F1244556983987888130&h=0e4a95f4\" target